text: Paravelleda bispinosa is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Per Olof Christopher Aurivillius in 1910.BioLib.cz - Paravelleda bispinosa. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Phrissomini Category:Beetles described in 1910
